APU Campus Connect Lounge will serve purposes for Arrival and Departure for all APU Shuttle Buses. 
The Lounge is located on Level 1 near the staff car park which could be access by lift and stairs at Block E. Do you want to know about the timetable?
APU Shuttle Busses will be ready at APU Campus Connect Lounge from time to time which located at Block E level 1. Want to know about the timetable?
